{"id": "ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4", "rating": 4.2, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 274, "displayName": {"text": "kodo", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBeFFWRjNiR1Y0TTBrdFlsQnpSbmRVVkdZMWRYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "A Michelin recognized restaurant that’s just perfect for a quiet evening. The atmosphere is chill and the playlist vey ear pleasing and well as the decor. Modern style design that’s chic and comfortable at the same time. We ordered the Wagyu Cheeseburger and Uni Pasta. Both of the dishes were good with flavor but the Uni pasta could’ve used a little more sauce but it’s a preference I guess. The cheeseburger came out looking like a hot mess but it delivered with flavor. The Basqu Cheesecake was the dessert we ordered and it was perfect with flavor and the presentation. Service was attentive and on point most of the time. So if you’re looking for a nice place to have a delicious bite or drinks then definitely check out this place, especially the gorgeous looking bar.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A Michelin recognized restaurant that’s just perfect for a quiet evening. The atmosphere is chill and the playlist vey ear pleasing and well as the decor. Modern style design that’s chic and comfortable at the same time. We ordered the Wagyu Cheeseburger and Uni Pasta. Both of the dishes were good with flavor but the Uni pasta could’ve used a little more sauce but it’s a preference I guess. The cheeseburger came out looking like a hot mess but it delivered with flavor. The Basqu Cheesecake was the dessert we ordered and it was perfect with flavor and the presentation. Service was attentive and on point most of the time. So if you’re looking for a nice place to have a delicious bite or drinks then definitely check out this place, especially the gorgeous looking bar.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Leonard AK", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117842202074880016182/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8nEH6Lmp1xWT31iGNFU0KIEVe8R46233iySSvChiGv7ZtfQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T16:12:51.534561692Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBeFFWRjNiR1Y0TTBrdFlsQnpSbmRVVkdZMWRYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBeFFWRjNiR1Y0TTBrdFlsQnpSbmRVVkdZMWRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77b86c05857:0x4ebd9556b971d767"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KS1ZHeDZObmxtWW05VU1HY3RSblEwYkc5SVdsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great Japanese restaurant with really nice ambiance, friendly and gracious staff. The host came up on a slow night to refill my wine, complimentary. It’s the kind of place that really values its customers and puts a lot of care into the food, unique cocktails and chill vibes. Great date spot or place to gather with friends at the bar. The karaage was delicious by the way.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great Japanese restaurant with really nice ambiance, friendly and gracious staff. The host came up on a slow night to refill my wine, complimentary. It’s the kind of place that really values its customers and puts a lot of care into the food, unique cocktails and chill vibes. Great date spot or place to gather with friends at the bar. The karaage was delicious by the way.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Matthew Bourhis", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109434077038230069417/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIhgc8rZ8vvZLIHMkapoEjrEkUEtMf6HsJHvv3kxjvUloNgq7E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-22T23:55:25.985501869Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KS1ZHeDZObmxtWW05VU1HY3RSblEwYkc5SVdsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KS1ZHeDZObmxtWW05VU1HY3RSblEwYkc5SVdsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77b86c05857:0x4ebd9556b971d767"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOUlMwMU5SRWhzUm14WE4yVnpXWE5tY0V4MGNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Dinner at Kodo was a wonderful experience. The atmosphere was stylish, cozy, and perfect for an evening out. The food was excellent, beautifully prepared and made with top quality ingredients. I highly recommend the Bluefin Tuna (sashimi platter) it was outstanding, and the Bluefin Tuna was impressively fresh and flavorful. The service was also attentive and friendly. I’ll definitely be coming back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Dinner at Kodo was a wonderful experience. The atmosphere was stylish, cozy, and perfect for an evening out. The food was excellent, beautifully prepared and made with top quality ingredients. I highly recommend the Bluefin Tuna (sashimi platter) it was outstanding, and the Bluefin Tuna was impressively fresh and flavorful. The service was also attentive and friendly. I’ll definitely be coming back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Feliz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115094546746670994955/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJk171zllf8zjZa4YD2jR3nvniFLQxcKWK_Orz9mL8WVawZWjz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-18T06:06:14.834255321Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOUlMwMU5SRWhzUm14WE4yVnpXWE5tY0V4MGNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOUlMwMU5SRWhzUm14WE4yVnpXWE5tY0V4MGNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77b86c05857:0x4ebd9556b971d767"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFRuWlZTM0pXYVhSdVYzWnlSMGRKU0Vsd2MzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Not often does a restaurant nail every detail, but Kodo did exactly that. We arrived a bit early for our reservation and were seated immediately—strong start.\n\nThe cocktail menu alone could have derailed the night. Too many great options, zero bad choices. Truly a “no notes” situation.\n\nWe ordered the ponzu oysters, eggplant, Brussels sprouts, broccolini (asked for it without the usual char—no hesitation, no awkward explanation, just executed perfectly), miso sea bass hand roll, toro sampler, toro carpaccio, chocolate torte, and the Basque cheesecake. Finished with two cappuccinos. Every single dish landed. No misses, no “this one’s just okay,” just consistently excellent food and flawless execution.\n\nCocktails were equally strong:\nSon of Kyushu – 10/10\nFuji Haze – 10/10 (that coconut foam is unreal)\nBeni Negroni – 10/10\nThe Kitsune – 10/10\n\nRating them felt like judging a perfect Olympic routine—no stumbles, no deductions.\n\nThe space deserves its own mention: minimalist, chic, and effortlessly classy. The photos online don’t do it justice—it feels even better in person.\n\nKodo is the kind of place that reminds you why dining out can still be exciting. Thoughtful service, beautiful food, and a vibe that feels special without trying too hard. Highly recommend. Fantastic date spot.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Not often does a restaurant nail every detail, but Kodo did exactly that. We arrived a bit early for our reservation and were seated immediately—strong start.\n\nThe cocktail menu alone could have derailed the night. Too many great options, zero bad choices. Truly a “no notes” situation.\n\nWe ordered the ponzu oysters, eggplant, Brussels sprouts, broccolini (asked for it without the usual char—no hesitation, no awkward explanation, just executed perfectly), miso sea bass hand roll, toro sampler, toro carpaccio, chocolate torte, and the Basque cheesecake. Finished with two cappuccinos. Every single dish landed. No misses, no “this one’s just okay,” just consistently excellent food and flawless execution.\n\nCocktails were equally strong:\nSon of Kyushu – 10/10\nFuji Haze – 10/10 (that coconut foam is unreal)\nBeni Negroni – 10/10\nThe Kitsune – 10/10\n\nRating them felt like judging a perfect Olympic routine—no stumbles, no deductions.\n\nThe space deserves its own mention: minimalist, chic, and effortlessly classy. The photos online don’t do it justice—it feels even better in person.\n\nKodo is the kind of place that reminds you why dining out can still be exciting. Thoughtful service, beautiful food, and a vibe that feels special without trying too hard. Highly recommend. Fantastic date spot.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Linda C.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108176874275005202730/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLO8-zTiDmuANoelTDEYV79ZIZlBjbhu_sAqZNxepjra6Y3Zg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-27T17:01:10.435379148Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFRuWlZTM0pXYVhSdVYzWnlSMGRKU0Vsd2MzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OWFRuWlZTM0pXYVhSdVYzWnlSMGRKU0Vsd2MzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77b86c05857:0x4ebd9556b971d767"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SdmNtaFVORlZ5ZWtvd1pYVkNNV05GZFZSaFRVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here for dinner and was blown away by the food—everything was delicious and full of flavor. It’s a bit on the expensive side, but overall well worth it. The service was top-notch, with excellent recommendations for both appetizers and drinks. The atmosphere was pleasant and quiet for a Sunday evening, which made it easy to relax and actually have a conversation without loud music.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here for dinner and was blown away by the food—everything was delicious and full of flavor. It’s a bit on the expensive side, but overall well worth it. The service was top-notch, with excellent recommendations for both appetizers and drinks. The atmosphere was pleasant and quiet for a Sunday evening, which made it easy to relax and actually have a conversation without loud music.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Daniel Perez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101595270702291163045/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWH9nOSmrtXo7smW81fdJCWm1X4t7x-CCtJ9vIiO97YbwnLELN3Tg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-21T16:46:19.847227324Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SdmNtaFVORlZ5ZWtvd1pYVkNNV05GZFZSaFRVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SdmNtaFVORlZ5ZWtvd1pYVkNNV05GZFZSaFRVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77b86c05857:0x4ebd9556b971d767"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJV1jAhnvHwoARZ9dxuVaVvU4/photos/AWCwydgcewyK-qUab-tV-7lVeru7IYSvpMSzYKawWHQH5TjvmxShk6XnQieIBddTMQ5BBC8QmFqFZ7qXUb1IhQdaXiXY-OwZfuns2svmm82fB5ilarOOqdWxe4p-fEgkv18-JSwoyCw2jfJiTg4bAd39qpocHdCNEwu3fcUS137TlAsjKbjJUw1Ofo3EoSets-5CmfOt8vVJyBE63MQo82FJHCyfwOG-VsVVkijUF9n7fuyCwiJxfVcV-OrXvRAZXBMZsG66JE1adnnXqjUZONIYHKZsAXzqKzDMurLcoBZ01jnpKunGxzqjFTlbi8VUqVrU4GJ93FK1b-YNmytubAOY0syWtlh87TPFyI3i9Wbp0IXCIEYwx17lH4RaHy55ffJOxgbPMdjvm-pQjxeQ7T6s72bq66o5ENlmOuq0B4DSNd_wg3Rv0sHdHoc_xwN3aNRe", "widthPx": 4